headlines.description: — Giannis Antetokounmpo tried to explain his early hot streak from the floor when — hey, wait a minute! — he saw himself in a commercial on a muted TV. Antetokounmpo interrupted his thought and praised actor Simu Liu and said he had a “kind heart.”
headlines.shortLinkText: Giannis scores 21, Matthews' 3 sends Bucks past 76ers 90-88

events.name: LA Clippers at Los Angeles Lakers

headlines.description: — Kawhi Leonard had 14 points and seven rebounds in his first game in 16 months, and the Los Angeles Clippers opened a season of sky-high expectations with a 103-97 victory over the Lakers on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Kawhi scores 14 in return, Clippers hold off Lakers 103-97
